Class IPNoOperationOption

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Loggable

    public final class IPNoOperationOption
extends IPSingleByteHeaderOption
    Represents an IP No-Operation Option (Option 1). Typically used to adjust alignment of subsequent options. The Type field has the following value: Copy=1|0, Class=0, Option=1 
     +-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+
 |?|0 0|0 0 0 0 1|
 +-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+
    Author:
    Gregory Bumgardner (gbumgard)
